
---

## 🚀 How to Deploy

1. **Fork or clone** this repository  
2. Go to **Settings → Pages**  
3. Under “Source”, choose `main` branch and root folder  
4. Save — your website will be live at:  
   👉 `https://<your-username>.github.io/<repo-name>/`

---

## 💡 Customization Tips

- Update your store name or logo in `index.html`  
- Change diamond prices or add categories easily  
- Modify colors and effects in `style.css`  
- Add more interactivity or animations in `script.js`  

---

## ⚙️ Technologies Used

- 🖥️ HTML5  
- 🎨 CSS3 (with neon glow effects)  
- ⚙️ JavaScript (Vanilla JS animations)  
- ☁️ GitHub Pages for hosting  

